/* ---------------------------------------------------------------------------*/

The Plugin offers the following metric :


- TotalCPUTimePercentage


/* ---------------------------------------------------------------------------*/

TotalCPUTimePercentage
----------------------

Metric Type     : Average
Sample Interval : 30 sec
CIM Data Type   : uint8
Units           : percent

Value Source    : the corresponding line of /proc/stat contains the CPU times
                  of this processor and are base for the calculation


